long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Visually marks current week at Google Calendar.
Make sure your gCalc UI is in English and you have enabled Settings -> View Options -> Show week numbers in your Calendar for this extension to work.
